## 9. Success Criteria

After Phase 2 ships:

- Home page clearly communicates "operating system for Sunday" positioning
- Services is findable, understandable, and visually prominent
- Central Control integration has a dedicated page that tech-sophisticated buyers can evaluate
- Pricing page makes the free/paid split obvious and the upgrade reason clear
- Tech Manager remains strong but is correctly positioned as a feature
- Overall site conveys a bigger, more cohesive product than it does today

Conversion metrics to track (baseline against current):
- Signup rate from home page
- Discovery call requests from Services and Central Control pages
- Pricing page exit rate (lower is better)
- Session depth (higher is better — indicates the IA is working)

